        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CL for comments [on <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Thinks Pangenesis would be important step in biology if admitted as probable.</p> 
<p>Introduction to French edition [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>] has injured the book.</p> 
